# Copy to .env.local and fill in. NEVER commit real values.
# The web app uses the ANON key only — never the service_role key.
#
# Find these in the Supabase dashboard: Settings -> API.
# The anon key is safe to ship to a browser bundle by Supabase's own design
# (RLS is the real access boundary, not key secrecy) — but this file still
# holds names only, never a real project's values, so a stale/rotated
# example never accidentally points a fresh checkout at someone else's data.

VITE_SUPABASE_URL=
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=

# Ingest service URL (defaults to http://localhost:8000 if unset)
# VITE_INGEST_URL=http://localhost:8000

# local | staging | production — affects display only (a non-production
# banner, log verbosity), never which database is used (that's decided by
# VITE_SUPABASE_URL above). Defaults to "local" if unset. See
# docs/ENVIRONMENT_VARIABLES.md.
# VITE_ENVIRONMENT=local

# MapTiler API key (https://cloud.maptiler.com/account/keys/) - powers the
# Map page's basemap switcher (Operational Dark, Satellite Hybrid, Terrain,
# Minimal Grey GIS). Unset -> only the free MapLibre demo style ("Operational
# Light") is available; the other modes render visibly disabled rather than
# silently failing. See docs/ENVIRONMENT_VARIABLES.md.
# VITE_MAPTILER_KEY=
